## Mission

Write tests that verify system behavior matches BDD scenarios and requirements.

## Scope

{{#if params.ac_id}}
AC-Scoped: Focus only on tests for {{params.ac_id}}.
{{else}}
Full scope: Cover all in-scope REQs and scenarios.
{{/if}}

## Context

{{#each inputs}}
- {{this}}
{{/each}}

## Constraints

- Do not weaken tests
- Do not implement features (tests only)
- No secrets
- Expected failures (pre-implementation) are acceptable
